en_507366_0	Three Governors and two new State Ministers have taken oaths before President Maithripala Sirisena.
en_507366_1	Rajith Keerthi Tennekoon took oaths as the Governor of the Central Province.
en_507366_2	Maitri Gunaratne has been appointed as the Governor of the Uva Province.
en_507366_3	Hemal Gunasekara took oaths as the Governor of the Southern Province.
en_507366_4	Meanwhile, Anoma Gamage took oaths as the new State Minister for Petroleum Resource Development while Lucky Jayawardena took oaths as the State Minister for City Planning, Water Supply and Higher Education before President Maithripala Sirisena.
